 the plane perpendicular to\ntranslation and (b) a buoyant reverse jet behind the particle that narrows as\nthe inverse square root of distance downstream.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Jul 2021 03:52:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-12"}
