 a careful analysis of the analytic continuation\nof their parameterizations. This requires the study of another limit equation\nin the complexified evolution variable, the so-called \\emph{inner equation}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Jul 2021 11:54:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 Feb 2023 15:02:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-27"}
